.ds Fx \fIHyla\s-1FAX\s+1\fP
.TH FAXADDUSER ${MANNUM1_8} "Aug 10, 1999"
.SH NAME
faxadduser \- add a fax user to the permissions file
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B ${SBIN}/faxadduser
[
.B \-a
.I admin-password
] [
.B \-f
.I permissions file
] [
.B \-h
.I host name
] [
.B \-p
.I password
] [
.B \-u
.I uid
] 
.I username
.SH DESCRIPTION
.I faxadduser
creates a new user for HylaFAX services, updating appropriate
permission files(see
.IR hosts.hfaxd (${MANNUM4_5})).
.PP
.SH OPTIONS
The following options are available:
.TP 10
.BI \-a " admin-password"
Password for the user to gain admin privileges.
.TP 10
.BI \-f " permissions-file"
Use a permissions file other than the default.
.TP 10
.BI \-h " host name"
Authenticate user from this host only.
.TP 10
.BI \-p " password"
Password for the user to access fax services.
.TP 10
.BI \-u " user-id"
User id number for user.
.SH "SEE ALSO"
.IR faxdeluser (${MANNUM1_8}),
.IR hosts.hfaxd (${MANNUM4_5}),
